ruleLogicalInfo.ruleDesc: There should not be dots in any of the DIAG_CDs in CLM_LINE table.

paramsVOLst.paramValue:
SEL * 
FROM #PRM_EDW_DATABASE#.CLM_LINE
WHERE
CLM_SOR_CD IN #PRM_CLM_SOR_CD#
AND ((#PRM_INCR_FLAG# = '2'
AND (  UPDTD_LOAD_LOG_KEY IN #PRM_UPDTD_LOAD_LOG_KEY_EDW# OR  LOAD_LOG_KEY IN #PRM_LOAD_LOG_KEY_EDW#)) 
OR(#PRM_INCR_FLAG# <> '2'AND (   UPDTD_LOAD_LOG_KEY IN #PRM_UPDTD_LOAD_LOG_KEY_EDW# 
OR   CRCTD_LOAD_LOG_KEY IN #PRM_CRCTD_LOAD_LOG_KEY_EDW# OR   LOAD_LOG_KEY IN #PRM_LOAD_LOG_KEY_EDW#)) 
OR (#PRM_DATAPROF_FLAG# = '2'))

AND (SUBSTR(PRNCPL_DIAG_CD,1,1) = '.'
OR SUBSTR(PRNCPL_DIAG_CD,2,1) = '.'
OR SUBSTR(PRNCPL_DIAG_CD,3,1) = '.'
OR SUBSTR(PRNCPL_DIAG_CD,4,1) = '.'
OR SUBSTR(PRNCPL_DIAG_CD,5,1) = '.'
OR SUBSTR(PRNCPL_DIAG_CD,6,1) = '.'
OR SUBSTR(PRNCPL_DIAG_CD,7,1) = '.'
OR SUBSTR(OTHR_DIAG_1_CD,1,1) = '.'
OR SUBSTR(OTHR_DIAG_1_CD,2,1) = '.'
OR SUBSTR(OTHR_DIAG_1_CD,3,1) = '.'
OR SUBSTR(OTHR_DIAG_1_CD,4,1) = '.'
OR SUBSTR(OTHR_DIAG_1_CD,5,1) = '.'
OR SUBSTR(OTHR_DIAG_1_CD,6,1) = '.'
OR SUBSTR(OTHR_DIAG_1_CD,7,1) = '.'
OR SUBSTR(OTHR_DIAG_2_CD,1,1) = '.'
OR SUBSTR(OTHR_DIAG_2_CD,2,1) = '.'
OR SUBSTR(OTHR_DIAG_2_CD,3,1) = '.'
OR SUBSTR(OTHR_DIAG_2_CD,4,1) = '.'
OR SUBSTR(OTHR_DIAG_2_CD,5,1) = '.'
OR SUBSTR(OTHR_DIAG_2_CD,6,1) = '.'
OR SUBSTR(OTHR_DIAG_2_CD,7,1) = '.'
OR SUBSTR(OTHR_DIAG_3_CD,1,1) = '.'
